    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super reliable for all my weekend getaways. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with all the maintenance, so it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road with its next owner! It drives so smoothly and has plenty of life left in it. I'd love for it to go to a good home\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
