    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 powerplant. This unit features a precision-shifted 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip variable M differential. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The naturally aspirated inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response, pulling strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Suspension geometry remains true with upgraded polyurethane bushings, providing sharp turn-in and excellent chassis communication. A well-sorted example for the discerning driver who values mechanical transparency and analog performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
