    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2014 Porsche 911 Carrera in a timeless Agate Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been my pride and joy, serving as a reliable and thrilling weekend driver. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though it shows minor, expected road wear such as small stone chips on the front bumper and a tiny scuff on the passenger side mirror housing. Inside, the black leather interior is remarkably supple; the bolsters show very light wear, and every switch, from the sunroof to the PCM system, functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is sound. It has received oil changes every 5,000 miles, and I recently replaced the brake pads and rotors. The PDK transmission shifts seamlessly, and the flat-six engine pulls strong through the entire rev range. It sits on 20-inch Carrera S wheels with plenty of tread remaining on the Michelin Pilot Sport tires. Includes a complete set of service records and two keys. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
